    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7999997635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依、お疲れ様\n貴方も自主トレ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ good job\nAre you also doing your own training?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8666673203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4666673203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、莉央さん。こんにちは\nそうです。貴方「も」ってことは、莉央さんも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rio-san. Hello\nThat's right. By 'you too' do you mean Rio-san‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4666673203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0333343685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。もう今日のメニューはこなしたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I've already completed today's menu",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0333343685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3000019253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "全然余裕そうですね\nあ、もし良かったら少し一緒に走りませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look relaxed\nAh‚ if you'd like‚ would you like go for a run together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3000019253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、いいわよ\nでも、私のペースについて来れるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ good\nBut‚ can you keep up with my pace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333352586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.5333373661
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.2000026882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "望むところです。むしろ、無理して莉央さんの方が\n音をあげないようにお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I want. Rather‚ I ask you to avoid making Rio-san\ncomplain by forcing yourself too hard",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2000026882,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.1500026882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……結構走ったわね\n10キロちょい、かしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… we ran quite a bit\nAbout 10km‚ I think…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8333416165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.0000067574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……そうですね。でも、まだまだ余裕です\nトリエルのリーダーとして、これくらい当然なので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… Yes. But‚ I still have some stamina left\nAs the leader of TRINITYAiLE‚ this much is natural",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0000067574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.8333400907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……言うじゃない。リズノワのメニューが\n過酷だってこと、見せつけてあげるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… You speak well. Let me show you\nhow difficult the menu at LizNoir is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8333400907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.866673424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ追加で20キロいくわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ let's go another 20km!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.866673424,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.341471400007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 75.3333461942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ぜぇ……はぁ……全然……はぁ、足りないですよ\n逆に……たぎって、きました………はぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not…. haa… enough… haa‚ at all\nOn the contrary… I'm on fire… haa‚ haa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666795275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 83.5000006994
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8666774931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私だって……た、足りないわ……\nこの程度で……後輩に……はぁ、負けないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-Me‚ too… n-not enough…\nThis is about it… for a junior… haa‚ don't give up",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8666774931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2333426339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのメニューはこんなもん、なんですか、ね？\nトリエルは………はぁ、はぁ……もっと、凄いですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this‚ the menu at‚ LizNoir?\nTRINITYAiLE is… haa‚ haa… more‚ awesome",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2333426339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 110.9666739328
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "こうなったらオーバーワーク上等よ……\n後輩に負けるなんて……あり得ないんだからっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ overwork is my answer…\nLosing to a junior… it doesn't make sense!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9666739328,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9966.6601
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.0833405994
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.6666734242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依も、さすがにもう諦めるでしょ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rui‚ will surely give up by now…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6666734242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さん、意地張ってないで）\n（疲れたって認めたらいいのに……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rio-san‚ don't be stubborn）\n（I wish you would admit that you're tired…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0333340328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.0333350047
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.2333400909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……え……\nいつの間にか日が暮れてるじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… eh…\nBefore we know it‚ the sun is setting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2333400909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.0666673661
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.1000098094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……六時間も走ってたら\n……日も暮れますよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… after six hours of running\n…sun will set‚ soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1000098094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.4000138783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "公園から都心部、神社、また公園に戻るルートって\nフルマラソンと同じ距離……走ってますから………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Route from the park to the city center‚ to the shrine‚ and back to the park is\nthe same distance… as a full marathon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4000138783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 155.5666866485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
